---
import AboutHeroImage from '../assets/blog-placeholder-about.jpg';
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="About"
	description="关于这个博客和它的作者"
	pubDate={new Date('May 27 2026')}
	heroImage={AboutHeroImage}
>
	<div data-i18n-zh>
		<p>
			嗨，我是 <strong>seizethe-day</strong>。
		</p>
		<p>
			这个博客叫 <em>Carpe Diem</em>（拉丁语「抓住今天」），用来记录我读过的书、写过的代码、走过的路、想过的事。文章不定期更新，长短随心。
		</p>
		<p>
			目前主要写中文，偶尔会用英文。右上角可以切换语言显示——切换的是网站界面，文章本身保持原语种。
		</p>
		<p>
			想找我聊聊：邮件 <a href="mailto:alice6161616@gmail.com">alice6161616@gmail.com</a>，或者 <a href="https://github.com/seizethe-day" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub</a>。
		</p>
		<p style="color: rgb(var(--gray)); font-size: 0.9em;">
			<em>这段「关于我」是占位文字，请编辑 <code>src/pages/about.astro</code> 替换成你想说的。</em>
		</p>
	</div>
	<div data-i18n-en>
		<p>
			Hi, I'm <strong>seizethe-day</strong>.
		</p>
		<p>
			This blog is called <em>Carpe Diem</em> (Latin for "seize the day"). I use it to record
			books I've read, code I've written, places I've been, and thoughts I've had. Posts come
			whenever; length is whatever.
		</p>
		<p>
			Most posts are in Chinese, some in English. Use the toggle in the top-right to switch the UI
			language — posts themselves stay in their original language.
		</p>
		<p>
			Reach me by <a href="mailto:alice6161616@gmail.com">email</a> or on <a
				href="https://github.com/seizethe-day"
				target="_blank"
				rel="noopener">GitHub</a
			>.
		</p>
		<p style="color: rgb(var(--gray)); font-size: 0.9em;">
			<em
				>This About page is a placeholder — edit <code>src/pages/about.astro</code> to make it yours.</em
			>
		</p>
	</div>
</Layout>
